tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE properties (
    property_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    property_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    neighborhood VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    square_feet INT NOT NULL,
    price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL
);
CREATE TABLE properties (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), neighborhood VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10,2), square_feet INT)
CREATE TABLE neighborhoods (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), average_price_per_sqft DECIMAL(10,2))

CREATE TABLE Property (
    property_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    property_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    neighborhood_id INT REFERENCES Neighborhood(neighborhood_id),
    property_type VARCHAR(50),
    property_size INT,
    price DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE Properties (
  property_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  neighborhood_id INT,
  property_type TEXT,
  square_feet INT,
  price INT
);

CREATE TABLE Calculations (
  calculation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  neighborhood_id INT,
  total_properties INT,
  total_price INT,
  average_price_per_sqft FLOAT
);
